MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping to extract data from SLBA_ITEM,STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE to populate SLBA_ITEM.
MAPPING.NAME: m_SLBA_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ITEM.ITEM_ID , TRIM(SLH.STYLE_NUM) , TRIM(SLH.HANES_BRAND_CODE), TRIM(ITEM.COMPANY_CODE) FROM SLBA_ITEM ITEM JOIN SLH_ITEM SLH ON ITEM.ITEM_ID=SLH.ITEM_ID WHERE TRIM(ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP) = 'slh'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: To update the target with WHOLESALE_PRICE based on ITEM_ID.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: UPD_SLBA_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRIM(STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE.WHOLESALE_PRICE) as WHOLESALE_PRICE, TRIM(STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE.BRAND_CODE) as BRAND_CODE, TRIM(STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE.STYLE_NUM) as STYLE_NUM, TRIM(STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE.PRICE_CODE) as PRICE_CODE FROM STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE WHERE TRUNC(SYSDATE) >=STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE.EFF_FROM_DATE AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) <=STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE.EFF_TO_DATE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: BRAND_CODE = I_BRAND_CODE AND STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE_NUM AND PRICE_CODE = I_PRICE_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Update Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: UPDATE STG_HS_STYLE_PRICE SET PROCESS_FLAG = :TU.PROCESS_FLAG, UPDATE_USERID = :TU.UPDATE_USERID, UPDATE_TIMESTAMP = :TU.UPDATE_TIMESTAMP WHERE BRAND_CODE = :TU.BRAND_CODE AND STYLE_NUM = :TU.STYLE_NUM

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: To update the target with WHOLESALE_PRICE based on ITEM_ID.
INSTANCE.NAME: UPD_SLBA_ITEM
